:144567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4297636d07fa23cf122019f0de009df338f4bd5","tid":892510,"uid":34810,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T00:54:29.000Z","msg":"你個三個point似係針對android喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T02:10:18.000Z","msg":"apple以外 全部都係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7480008b93accfbc8ab82915f01a47f66eaf337a","tid":892510,"uid":155525,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T02:38:50.000Z","msg":"我不嬲都雙修，唔會為左一個品牌放棄其他正野，分別只係你用蘋果定Android 做主機，我有八仔sim 所以android 一定會做主機，樓主講得好啱，舊iPhone 都好順，如果只係當玩具玩吓，真係冇問題，但玩game 電一定倒水，所以買部二手 6 plus 上ios 12 就OK ，至於用唔用大陸機，只係對比番android 有乜新機可以揀，唔係蘋果vs 大陸機，因為蘋果正係一部不折不扣大陸機。"},{"pid":"121305e58748cad0204f7060fefaa227a2ef2340","tid":892510,"uid":7343,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T10:41:07.000Z","msg":"平，可以刷ROM <br />\n通常大電 硬件好"},{"pid":"a20dd1c31920dc9099d2e3a3c992334f811107fb","tid":892510,"uid":181379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T11:29:50.000Z","msg":"平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}